flowchart TD
    WAL[WAL Reader\nPostgresLogicalReplicationClient]
    DEC[PgOutput Decoder\nPgOutputMessageDecoder]
    NORM[Event Normaliser\nEventNormalizer]
    WC[Watermark Coordinator\nWatermarkCoordinator]
    REC[Reconciliation Engine\nReconciliationEngine]
    DEL[Delivery Coordinator\nDeliveryCoordinator]
    SINK[Event Sink\nEventSink]

    WAL -->|raw pgoutput bytes| DEC
    DEC -->|typed replication message| NORM
    NORM -->|ChangeEnvelope| WC
    WC -->|windowed events + chunk rows| REC
    REC -->|merged event sequence| DEL
    DEL -->|acknowledged publish| SINK
